0:03 Did you know that when fans go to The Cliff Cafe and Pub in Jeju Island they look around to see if they can find Sana's lost Butterfly blue hair ribbon?
It is true!
Somewhere in the cafe or outside is Sana's Butterfly  blue hair ribbon
She wore it at the beginning of the video where she turns around and looks into the camera.
During the day, she took the ribbon off and laid it down and lost it.
For the night filming she had to wear a ponytail because the staff could not find the ribbon, even though they looked everywhere.
There is even a reward for the lost Butterfly blue hair ribbon, yet no one has found it to claim the reward.
So if you ever visit The Cliff Cafe and Pub in Jeju Island where Alcohol Free was filmed, look around, you just may find the Butterfly ribbon and claim the reward.
